{"questionId":"25618","questionHtml":"<p>Hence, given that <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>arg</mtext><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math>, find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>arg</mtext><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>1</mn></msub><msub><mi>z</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mtext>arctan</mtext><mfenced><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow><mrow><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfrac></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><br><strong>EITHER</strong><br><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>arctan</mtext><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow></mfenced><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi><mn>4</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp;(since&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>≠</mo><mn>0</mn></math>, for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>∈</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">ℝ</mi></math>)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><br><strong>OR</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>-</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>-</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></math>&nbsp; (or equivalent)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><br><strong>THEN</strong></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"25618","referenceCode":"22M.1.AHL.TZ1.9b","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Hence, given that argz1z2=π4, find the value of b.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3— Geometry and trigonometry","SL 3.5—Unit circle definitions of sin, cos, tan. Exact trig ratios, ambiguous case of sine rule"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}